text: The Singapore Pro Wrestling is a professional wrestling promotion based in Singapore. It also has a wrestling school for those who want to learn professional wrestling and become a professional wrestler in the future. It is currently one of the top wrestling promotions in Southeast Asia and has competed in an inter-promotion contest against other top Asia's promotions such as the Dragon Gate. ==Reference== https://www.cagematch.net/?id=8&nr;=1139 https://www.straitstimes.com/singapore/singapores-pro-wrestling-shows-pull-in- crowds https://www.spw.com.sg/ Category:Professional wrestling promotions Category:Companies of Singapore
